{"tid":1039346,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【同屆冠軍朱晨麗】「洋洋」劉思希好學不倦 攻讀科大全球第一EMBA課程","createTime":"2019-02-27T10:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T10:52:18.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54e54512b55527b124866b2b73b2144a524310ec","tid":1039346,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"曾參選過2011年港姐的無綫藝員劉思希，在處境劇《愛‧回家之開心速遞》飾演「洋洋」，備受網民留意，她除了邊工作後，還忙在科大讀書，修讀科大EMBA課程，工作學業兩邊忙，據悉劉思希所讀的課程相當厲害，在全球EMBA課程，連續三年排首位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190227/s00009/ca5b7cc7bb18c4c5bfffca475976ed5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190227%2Fs00009%2Fca5b7cc7bb18c4c5bfffca475976ed5c.jpg&h=c0943d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉思希本月初曾在社交網上載溫書照，她曾說：「在化妝間等埋位的時間最好做什麼呢？案係...爭取時間溫書！因為新年過後要拍劇，兩科考試同一大堆功課哦 搞掂埋你地（哋），讓我開開心心過年吧~! 最後衝刺加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dJ6hEyGzipA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FdJ6hEyGzipA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=aff437c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/235184_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F235184_1.png&h=cdba0b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://staffabands.top/uploads/large/WVVoU01HTkViM1pNTTJRelpIazFkR0ZYTlc1alIwWjJXVEpHZFZsWFVtaE1iVTUyWWxNNVZWUXhTWFphYmxKM1REQTFiR1F6VFhaTmFrRjRUbnBCTkUxRVVYWlRSWE4yV0hwQk1GUlZSWGROUkZabVRHMXdkMXAz/%E8%B8%A9%E9%81%8E%E7%95%8C-%E7%8E%8B%E6%B5%A9%E4%BF%A1-%E6%9C%B1%E5%8D%83%E9%9B%AA-%E6%84%9B%E8%BF%91%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%BC%E5%89%8D/%E6%9C%B1%E5%8D%83%E9%9B%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%A7%8D%E6%AE%BA-%E7%8E%8B%E6%B5%A9%E4%BF%A1%E6%94%AC%E5%B1%8D%E5%93%AD%E5%B4%A9-%E8%B8%A9%E9%81%8E%E7%95%8C-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E6%9D%8E%E4%BD%B3%E8%8A%AF%E5%A2%AE%E5%B4%96%E6%85%98%E6%AD%BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2